{"tid":1496953,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[超有心推頂置］慣左啊！唔慣啊？要慣啦！","createTime":"2019-08-22T17:51:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T17:43:49.000Z","uid":39771,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ad8008f41d8902da92637b835412bd1044176f95","tid":1496953,"uid":39771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:51:14.000Z","msg":"（2014）開始：<br />\n黑警放催淚彈 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 哇，放催淚彈都有既<br />\n黑警開布袋彈 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 哇，竟然開槍射人民<br />\n黑警亂咁打人 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 哇，無皇法咩咁打人<br />\n<br />\n（2019）現在：<br />\n黑警放催淚彈 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 唉，香港人免疫架啦<br />\n黑警開布袋彈 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 唉，個女仔真係慘啊<br />\n黑警亂咁打人 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 唉，痴線咩咁樣打人<br />\n<br />\n係啊<br />\n<br />\n本身覺得好不可思議既事原來慣左就得架啦？<br />\n<br />\n成日叫人唔好慣左黑警既行動方式<br />\n<br />\n咁不如叫人民慣左我地既行動方式啦<br />\n<br />\n慢慢慢慢就唔會覺架啦大家知道未？<br />\n<br />\n人民開始：<br />\n勇武開始攻立法會 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 哇，破壞公物都有既<br />\n勇武開始反攻黑警 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 哇，無論點唔好還手<br />\n勇武士假設要進攻 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 哇，點可以破壞法治<br />\n<br />\n人民現在：<br />\n勇武開始攻立法會 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 岩，要比啲顏色佢地<br />\n勇武開始反攻黑警 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 岩，要對對黑警還手<br />\n勇武士假設要進攻 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 岩，唔好比人食住上<br />\n<br />\n對上一日睇完烏克蘭段片好多人都覺得好似<br />\n<br />\n一開始其實都好似，但政府背景唔同唔可以作比較<br />\n<br />\n但我地唔可以輸架，啲義士點樣算？<br />\n<br />\n唔岩聽都要講，點解會有咁多人係8.18行出黎？<br />\n<br />\n就係因為勇武大哥做完野，啲人覺得心有不甘<br />\n<br />\n如果無勇武仲會咁多人行出黎咩！？！？！？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">與其叫人唔好習慣黑警既方式<br />\n<br />\n不如市民習慣我地既方式<br />\n<br />\n其實市民或者政府都開始習慣<br />\n<br />\n因為由一開始佔馬路到左而家係最低消費既道理一樣！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">最後要打番幾隻字<br />\n<br />\n就係啲五毛或者三毛以為打左就唔係鬼既字<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">真香港人一生平安<br />\n<br />\n希望我地可以好似烏克蘭結局一樣</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">榮耀歸於香港<br />\n<br />\n榮耀歸於英雄  </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">希望各位可以幫我推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"76c7a6230632e6aa28dedef6b7f589e9ad83574a","tid":1496953,"uid":39771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:51:45.000Z","msg":"無論有冇人推都好，我都會自己幫自己推上去"},{"pid":"45dc4063476c630ef96a7d9e134a9187d9946ec9","tid":1496953,"uid":39771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:51:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"492a7ad54070444be68490ccece568e319a31e72","tid":1496953,"uid":39771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:52:10.000Z","msg":"2推"},{"pid":"786ddd1d60d880161572dde9a2cda42b23c969a3","tid":1496953,"uid":39771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:52:22.000Z","msg":"3推"},{"pid":"9b5c3ae82be5af397a1099914ed386c79c17e785","tid":1496953,"uid":39771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:52:35.000Z","msg":"4推"},{"pid":"7d310465cb9d25197c24eed0180d4f05b52add96","tid":1496953,"uid":39771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:52:48.000Z","msg":"5推"},{"pid":"3e07420628d5dd2541ed48665a6e80869878a2b4","tid":1496953,"uid":39771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:52:59.000Z","msg":"6推"},{"pid":"8d784f02bce46d7d886d5ac44af5727253a1553d","tid":1496953,"uid":39771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:53:12.000Z","msg":"7推"},{"pid":"b43fb919160eda81e4ce2dc6b9db345c794af193","tid":1496953,"uid":39771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:53:24.000Z","msg":"8推"},{"pid":"85107201bd2bd1eb23e8431cefcd00bcae511a0a","tid":1496953,"uid":39771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:53:37.000Z","msg":"9推"},{"pid":"de991953d7853f495735dd9ca868dac33ce117fe","tid":1496953,"uid":39771,"li